ception-1749460243 in class hipstershop.AdService,出现次数:1\r\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["frontend-0", "frontend-2", "frontend-1", "adservice-0", "adservice-2", "adservice-1"], "service_name": ["frontend", "adservice"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-03", "aiops-k8s-04", "aiops-k8s-07", "aiops-k8s-08"]}, "matched_anomaly": "A fault was detected from 2025-06-09T09:10:42Z to 2025-06-09T09:25:42Z. Please analyze its root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-09 09:10:42+00:00 to 2025-06-09 09:25:42+00:00"}, "log_data_collected": true, "metric_analysis_findings": "根据采集到的数据，我们可以分析以下异常情况：\n\n### 异常指标总结\n\n1. **服务性能**\n   - `paymentservice`: 服务的最大响应时间(`rrt_max`)在故障期间显著增加，`change_ratio` 最高达到 **1.7208**。\n   - `shippingservice`: 服务的最大响应时间(`rrt_max`)也显著增加，`change_ratio` 达到 **1.4433**。\n   - `cartservice`: 服务的最大响应时间(`rrt_max`)增加，`change_ratio` 达到 **0.6562**。\n   \n2. **节点内存**\n   - `aiops-k8s-03`: `node_memory_usage_rate` 从正常的 34.44% 增加到 52.62%，`change_ratio` 为 **0.4176**。\n\n### 异常 Pod 和节点映射\n\n1. **Pod 和节点**\n   - `shippingservice-2` 运行在 `aiops-k8s-03`\n   - `paymentservice-1` 运行在 `aiops-k8s-03`\n   - `cartservice-2` 运行在 `aiops-k8s-08`\n\n### 分析结论\n\n初步分析表明，`aiops-k8s-03` 节点的内存使用增加是导致多个服务性能下降的主要原因，尤其是`paymentservice`和`shippingservice`的性能显著受到影响。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"node_memory_usage_rate\",\n    \"rrt\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-03\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_memory_usage_rate increase causing degradation in paymentservice and shippingservice performance\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_usage_rate increased from 34.44% to 52.62%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"High rrt_max due to node memory constraints\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max increased from 2893.0ms to 3183.0ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"High rrt_max due to node memory constraints\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max increased from 2513.0ms to 3207.0ms\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "log_analysis_findings": "已成功获取相关时间段内的日志数据，现在进入分析阶段，提取关键错误信息和异常调用链。请稍后，结果马上就来。\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\n    \"rpc error\",\n    \"code = Unknown\",\n    \"failed to retrieve ads\",\n    \"AdService-getRandomAds-exception\",\n    \"java.lang.Error\",\n    \"Injected error\",\n    \"java.lang.Exception\",\n    \"Byteman agent\",\n    \"connection refused\",\n    \"Transformer\",\n    \"RuleTriggerMethodAdapter\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"The frontend service encountered repeated gRPC errors, failing to retrieve ads from the adservice. Log messages mention 'rpc error: code = Unknown desc = ', indicating issues during call operations.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Log snippet: '{\\\"error\\\":\\\"failed to get ads: rpc error: code = Unknown desc = \\\"...'\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Multiple logs from adservice indicate exceptions triggered during the execution of getRandomAds() method. Mentions of 'java.lang.Error: Injected error' and 'Byteman agent' suggest artificial faults or misconfigurations.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Log snippet: 'Exception in thread \\\"grpc-default-executor-8140\\\" java.lang.Error: Injected error'\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Byteman agent-related logs suggest potential repetitious trigger insertion attempts, which could destabilize the adservice component.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Log snippet: 'Attempting to load Byteman agent more than once'\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n``` \n\n这份分析结果从日志中提取了关键的错误信息，表明问题可能始于 `adservice` 服务，并与其调用链相互牵连，导致 `frontend` 服务功能受限。", "trace_analysis_findings": "我已成功获取有关异常的数据。以下是两个不同请求中处理到的结果的汇总：\n\n### 显著延迟的调用链分析：\n\n1. **CartService 的延迟**\n   - `CartService` 的 `AddItem` 操作和 `GetCart` 操作在正常和异异常情况下持续时间分别有显著差异。\n   - **前端调用 CartService 的 AddItem 操作**\n     - 正常平均耗时: 3982 ms\n     - 异常平均耗时: 37344 ms\n     - 延迟倍数: 9.38\n\n2. **Redis 访问延迟**\n   - `Redis` 的 `HGET` 和 `HMSET` 操作在异常时段的持续时间明显增加。\n   - `HGET` 操作:\n     - 正常平均耗时: 1553 ms\n     - 异常平均耗时: 19470 ms\n     - 延迟倍数: 12.54\n\n3. **ProductCatalogService 的延迟**\n   - `CheckoutService` 调用 `ProductCatalogService` 的 `GetProduct` 操作\n     - 正常平均耗时: 10548 ms\n     - 异常平均耗时: 20507 ms\n     - 延迟倍数: 1.95\n\n4. **其他显著延迟调用**\n   - `ShippingService` 有多个不同的操作都表现出延迟，包括 `GetQuote` 和 `ShipOrder`。\n\n### 错误状态组合：\n\n- 主要错误出现于 `frontend` 服务在调用 `AdService` 时发生了大量的状态码 `2`。\n  - `frontend` 在 `AdService` 上报出 1570 次状态码 `2`。\n  - 此问题可能反映了某种调用失败或拒绝。\n\n### 组件延迟和错误影响的痕迹：\n\n- `CartService` 和 `Redis` 在调用过程中均表现出显著的延迟，暗示问题可能集中在 `Cart` 操作环节。\n- 服务链最显著的延迟出现在 `CartService` 与其后端的 `Redis` 交互中。\n\n### 结论：\n\n显著的 `CartService` 和 `Redis` 延迟表明这可能是根因，影响到了上游 `CheckoutService` 及其他调用链。需要进一步检查 `Redis` 和 `CartService` 的交互，以追踪延迟根因。\n\n### 输出 JSON：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\",\n    \"frontend->cartservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CartService\",\n      \"reason\": \"CartService 在从前端进行 AddItem 操作时有显著延迟。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"延迟倍数: 9.38\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"Redis 在处理来自 CartService 的请求时表现出高级延迟。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"HGET 延迟倍数: 12.54\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n进一步的分析可以聚焦于这些异常的负载处理和数据交互上，以鉴别具体根因并优化性能。"}
